The evidence with the title 'Why the US has the most mass shootings - CNN ' says Oct 5, 2017  ... ( CNN ) when it comes to gun massacres , the United States is tragically exceptional : there are more public mass shootings in the United States than in any other country in the world , according to a study publishedrecently.Between 1966 and 2012 , there were 90 mass shootings in the United States. 
